title: This Bud Dupree's For You
description:
Mina talks to Chris Long about Carson Wentz' fit in Indy, who the Patriots should target to be their quarterback next season, and where the top free agents like Trent Williams, Kenny Golladay, Leonard Williams, Yannick Ngakoue, and Bud Dupree will wind up.
